Ta tahab mind sinu juurde.

1264
01:33:55.109 --> 01:33:57.945
- Imelik sitt.
- Kurat!

1265
01:33:58.029 --> 01:33:59.572
Mida kuradit?

1266
01:33:59.655 --> 01:34:01.991
